             were indicted for <rs id="t18240916-215-off1156" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240916-215-off1156" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240916-215-off1156" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240916-215-cd1157" type="crimeDate">16th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-215-off1156 t18240916-215-cd1157"></join>, a writing desk, value 10 s., and a candlestick, value 5 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240916-215-victim1783" type="victimName">
                     Thomas Stammers 
                     Alger
                  <interp inst="t18240916-215-victim1783" type="surname" value="Alger"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240916-215-victim1783" type="given" value="Thomas Stammers"></interp>
